snippet.title: Godzilla Extended Trailer + Trailer Review - 2014 : HD PLUS

localized.description:
Godzilla debuts an extended trailer for 2014!  Watch it today with a trailer review!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Godzilla debuts an extended trailer for 2014 and you can see it here today plus get a trailer review!  Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph gives you her reaction to this new extended trailer for Godzilla starring Bryan Cranston, Aaron Taylor Johnson, Elizabeth Olsen and Ken Watanabe, from Legendary Pictures!  Is this movie authentic enough to its origins in Japan?  And with Beyond The Trailer's Trailer Plus, you'll get a link to other movie news, reviews, and trailers!  Enjoy this extended HD trailer and trailer review for Godzilla before you see the full movie in 2014!  And make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for entertainment news on YouTube today!
